## 2) System Goal (Frozen)
Build a lumbar-mounted athlete monitoring data logger for running-focused fatigue analysis, combining:
- BMI270 IMU (biomechanics)
- BMP390 barometer (terrain gradient context)
- u-blox MAX-10S GNSS (route + absolute timing + multi-device sync)
- SD logging over SPI (primary storage)

Primary use:
- Post-process synchronized data to detect fatigue onset and progression.
- Later support multi-node setups (e.g., lumbar + tibia units) with GNSS time alignment.

